###
### QUICK REFERENCE - HOW TO USE
###

# 1. Install VS Code Extension:
#    REST Client (by Huachao Mao)

# 2. Open this file in VS Code

# 3. Hover over any request and click "Send Request"

# 4. Response appears in the sidebar

# 5. To use JWT token:
#    a. Run register endpoint
#    b. Copy verificationToken from response
#    c. Paste into verify-email request
#    d. Run verify-email endpoint
#    e. Run login endpoint
#    f. Copy accessToken from response
#    g. Replace PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual token
#    h. Now you can test all admin endpoints

# 6. To get user ID:
#    - Run GET /users or create user endpoint
#    - Copy _id from response
#    - Paste into other endpoints like GET /users/:id

###
